{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.1","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:1","prev_osis_id":"Lev.021.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Cas o\u00f9 il est d\u00e9fendu de manger des victimes consacr\u00e9es. Choix des victimes pour les sacrifices<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-9: cf. L\u00e9 7:19-21. (1 Co 11:28-30.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel parla \u00e0 Mo\u00efse, et dit:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.2","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:2","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.21.24","name":"L\u00e9vitique 21:24","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.21.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.2","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:2","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Parle \u00e0 Aaron et \u00e0 ses fils, afin qu\u2019ils s\u2019abstiennent des choses saintes qui me sont consacr\u00e9es par les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, et qu\u2019ils ne profanent point mon saint nom. Je suis l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.1","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:1","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.3","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:3","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Dis-leur: Tout homme parmi vos descendants et de votre race, qui s\u2019approchera des choses saintes que consacrent \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, et qui aura sur lui quelque impuret\u00e9, cet homme-l\u00e0 sera retranch\u00e9 de devant moi. Je suis l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.2","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:2","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.4","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:4","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Tout homme de la race d\u2019Aaron, qui aura la l\u00e8pre ou une gonorrh\u00e9e, ne mangera point des choses saintes jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce qu\u2019il soit pur. Il en sera de m\u00eame pour celui qui touchera une personne souill\u00e9e par le contact d\u2019un cadavre, pour celui qui aura une pollution,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.3","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:3","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.5","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:5","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>pour celui qui touchera un reptile et en aura \u00e9t\u00e9 souill\u00e9, ou un homme atteint d\u2019une impuret\u00e9 quelconque et en aura \u00e9t\u00e9 souill\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.6","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:6","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.4","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:4","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.6","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:6","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Celui qui touchera ces choses sera impur jusqu\u2019au soir; il ne mangera pas des choses saintes, mais il lavera son corps dans l\u2019eau;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.7","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:7","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.5","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:5","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.7","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:7","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>apr\u00e8s le coucher du soleil, il sera pur, et il mangera ensuite des choses saintes, car c\u2019est sa nourriture.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.8","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:8","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.6","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:6","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.8","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:8","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Il ne mangera point d\u2019une b\u00eate morte ou d\u00e9chir\u00e9e, afin de ne pas se souiller par elle. Je suis l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.9","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:9","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.7","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:7","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.9","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:9","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Ils observeront mes commandements, de peur qu\u2019ils ne portent la peine de leur p\u00e9ch\u00e9 et qu\u2019ils ne meurent, pour avoir profan\u00e9 les choses saintes. Je suis l\u2019\u00c9ternel, qui les sanctifie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.10","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:10","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.8","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:8","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.10","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:10","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.011,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 10-16: cf. No 18:8-19. Mt 7:6.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Aucun \u00e9tranger ne mangera des choses saintes; celui qui demeure chez un sacrificateur et le mercenaire ne mangeront point des choses saintes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.11","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:11","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.9","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:9","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.11","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:11","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Mais un esclave achet\u00e9 par le sacrificateur \u00e0 prix d\u2019argent pourra en manger, de m\u00eame que celui qui est n\u00e9 dans sa maison; ils mangeront de sa nourriture.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.12","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:12","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.10","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:10","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.12","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:12","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>La fille d\u2019un sacrificateur, mari\u00e9e \u00e0 un \u00e9tranger, ne mangera point des choses saintes offertes par \u00e9l\u00e9vation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.13","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:13","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.11","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:11","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.13","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:13","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Mais la fille d\u2019un sacrificateur qui sera veuve ou r\u00e9pudi\u00e9e, sans avoir d\u2019enfants, et qui retournera dans la maison de son p\u00e8re comme dans sa jeunesse, pourra manger de la nourriture de son p\u00e8re. Aucun \u00e9tranger n\u2019en mangera.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.12","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:12","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.14","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:14","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Si un homme mange involontairement d\u2019une chose sainte, il donnera au sacrificateur la valeur de la chose sainte, en y ajoutant un cinqui\u00e8me.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.15","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:15","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.13","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:13","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.15","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:15","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Les sacrificateurs ne profaneront point les choses saintes qui sont pr\u00e9sent\u00e9es par les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, et qu\u2019ils ont offertes par \u00e9l\u00e9vation \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.16","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:16","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.14","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:14","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.16","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:16","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>ils les chargeraient ainsi du p\u00e9ch\u00e9 dont ils se rendraient coupables en mangeant les choses saintes: car je suis l\u2019\u00c9ternel, qui les sanctifie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.17","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:17","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.15","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:15","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.17","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:17","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.018,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 17-25: cf. De 17:1. Mal 1:8, 13, 14. 2 S 24:24.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel parla \u00e0 Mo\u00efse, et dit:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.18","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:18","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.16","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:16","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.18","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:18","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Parle \u00e0 Aaron et \u00e0 ses fils, et \u00e0 tous les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, et tu leur diras: Tout homme de la maison d\u2019Isra\u00ebl ou des \u00e9trangers en Isra\u00ebl, qui offrira un holocauste \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, soit pour l\u2019accomplissement d\u2019un v\u0153u, soit comme offrande volontaire,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.19","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:19","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.17","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:17","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.19","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:19","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>prendra un m\u00e2le sans d\u00e9faut parmi les b\u0153ufs, les agneaux ou les ch\u00e8vres, afin que sa victime soit agr\u00e9\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.20","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:20","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.18","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:18","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.20","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:20","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Vous n\u2019en offrirez aucune qui ait un d\u00e9faut, car elle ne serait pas agr\u00e9\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.21","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:21","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.19","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:19","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.21","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:21","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Si un homme offre \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel du gros ou du menu b\u00e9tail en sacrifice d\u2019actions de gr\u00e2ces, soit pour l\u2019accomplissement d\u2019un v\u0153u, soit comme offrande volontaire, la victime sera sans d\u00e9faut, afin qu\u2019elle soit agr\u00e9\u00e9e; il n\u2019y aura en elle aucun d\u00e9faut.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.20","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:20","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.22","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:22","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Vous n\u2019en offrirez point qui soit aveugle, estropi\u00e9e, ou mutil\u00e9e, qui ait des ulc\u00e8res, la gale ou une dartre; vous n\u2019en ferez point sur l\u2019autel un sacrifice consum\u00e9 par le feu devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.23","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:23","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.21","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:21","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.23","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:23","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Tu pourras sacrifier comme offrande volontaire un b\u0153uf ou un agneau ayant un membre trop long ou trop court, mais il ne sera point agr\u00e9\u00e9 pour l\u2019accomplissement d\u2019un v\u0153u.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.24","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:24","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.24","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:24","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Vous n\u2019offrirez point \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel un animal dont les testicules ont \u00e9t\u00e9 froiss\u00e9s, \u00e9cras\u00e9s, arrach\u00e9s ou coup\u00e9s; vous ne l\u2019offrirez point en sacrifice dans votre pays.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.25","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:25","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.23","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:23","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.25","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:25","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Vous n\u2019accepterez de l\u2019\u00e9tranger aucune de ces victimes, pour l\u2019offrir comme aliment de votre Dieu; car elles sont mutil\u00e9es, elles ont des d\u00e9fauts: elles ne seraient point agr\u00e9\u00e9es.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.26","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:26","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.24","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:24","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.26","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:26","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.027,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 26-33: cf. Ex 22:30. L\u00e9 7:15-18.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel dit \u00e0 Mo\u00efse:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.27","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:27","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.25","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:25","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.27","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:27","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Un b\u0153uf, un agneau ou une ch\u00e8vre, quand il na\u00eetra, restera sept jours avec sa m\u00e8re; d\u00e8s le huiti\u00e8me jour et les suivants, il sera agr\u00e9\u00e9 pour \u00eatre offert \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel en sacrifice consum\u00e9 par le feu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.28","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:28","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.26","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:26","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.28","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:28","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>B\u0153uf ou agneau, vous n\u2019\u00e9gorgerez pas un animal et son petit le m\u00eame jour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.29","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:29","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.27","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:27","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.29","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:29","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Quand vous offrirez \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel un sacrifice d\u2019actions de gr\u00e2ces, vous ferez en sorte qu\u2019il soit agr\u00e9\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.30","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:30","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.28","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:28","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.30","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:30","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>La victime sera mang\u00e9e le jour m\u00eame; vous n\u2019en laisserez rien jusqu\u2019au matin. Je suis l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.31","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:31","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.29","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:29","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.31","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:31","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Vous observerez mes commandements, et vous les mettrez en pratique. Je suis l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.32","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:32","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.30","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:30","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.32","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:32","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.022.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Vous ne profanerez point mon saint nom, afin que je sois sanctifi\u00e9 au milieu des enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl. Je suis l\u2019\u00c9ternel, qui vous sanctifie,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.33","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:33","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.31","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:31","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.33","label":"","reference":"L\u00e9vitique 22:33","prev_osis_id":"Lev.022.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Lev.023.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Lev.22.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>et qui vous ai fait sortir du pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte pour \u00eatre votre Dieu. Je suis l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Lev.22","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.23.1","name":"L\u00e9vitique 23:1","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.23.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Lev.22.32","name":"L\u00e9vitique 22:32","id":"fra-LSG:Lev.22.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript